claim.claim-text:
17. A network interconnected server comprising: 
a processor; 
a network interface in communication with a data network and said processor; 
persistent storage memory in communication with said processor, and storing processor readable instructions that adapt said server to, 
a. maintain a database of identifiers of network interconnected computing device; 
b. receive a message from a network interconnected computing device using said network interface, said message comprising an identifier of said computing device; 
c. query said database using said identifier; and 
d. provide, to said network based computing device using said interface, an address of a network interconnected server for providing service to said interconnected computing device.

18. A network interconnected computing device, comprising: 
a processor; 
a network interface in communication with a data network and said processor; 
persistent storage memory in communication with said processor, and storing processor readable instructions that adapt said device to, 
a. contact a first network server having a first network address, using said network interface; 
b. provide said first network server with an identifier of said computing device; 
c. obtain from said first network server a second identifier of a network server, provided by said first network server based on said identifier provided in step b; and 
d. provide said network server identified by said second identifier with an identifier of said computer to obtain network services from said second network server.

19. A network interconnected server comprising: 
means for maintaining a database of identifiers of network interconnected computing device; 
means for receiving a message from a network interconnected computing device, said message comprising an identifier of said computing device; 
means for querying said database using said identifier; and means for providing to said network based computing device, an address of a network interconnected server based on said identifier.

20. A computer readable medium comprising a software program that when loaded into a computer adapts said computer to: 
a. maintain a database of identifiers of network interconnected computing devices; 
b. receive a message from a network interconnected computing device, said message comprising an identifier of said computing device; 
c. query said database using said identifier; and 
d. provide to said network based computing device, an address of a network interconnected server, based on said identifier.
